import React from 'react'
import {Container} from './style'
const Reklama = () => {
    return (
        <Container>
             <Card>
                 <Img/>
                 <Title>Free Shipping</Title>
                 <Desc>Orders over $100</Desc>
             </Card>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Reklama
